        {
            "title": "中國3月CPI跌0.1% PPI跌2.5% 均遜預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/54b11c6d8e68fc7ea5761c71a9cc57aa/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250410/_2025041009451370990.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中國通脹及工業生產物價受季節性因素影響而下降，據國家統計局公佈，3月居民消費價格指數（CPI）按年跌0.1%，按月跌0.4%；工業生產者出廠價格指數（PPI）按年下降2.5%，按月下降0.4%。\n\n</p>\n<p>兩項數字均遜預期，市場原先預期CPI會上升0.1%，PPI則預期會下降2.3%。\n\n</p>\n<p>國統局表示，CPI及PPI下降，主要受季節性、國際輸入性因素等影響。從邊際變化看，提振消費需求等政策效應進一步顯現，扣除食品和能源價格的核心CPI明顯回升，按年由上月下降0.1%轉為上漲0.5%。局方指，供需結構有所改善，價格呈現一些積極變化。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063124/即時-財經-中國3月CPI跌0-1-PPI跌2-5-均遜預期",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 09:51:31",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "龍翔道貨車冒煙  現場濃煙密佈",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4f7f81519218ba1f742b96537c9320cf/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250410/_2025041009411845366.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（10日）晨9時許，一輛黃色貨車沿龍翔道往荃灣方向行駛，途至龍翔道公園對開發生機件故障，車身冒煙，導致現場濃煙密佈，尾隨車輛紛紛停車，受事故影響，現場交通受阻。\n\n</p>\n<p>運輸署公布，因車輛故障，龍翔道(往荃灣方向)近龍翔道公園的部份行車線現已封閉，駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車，現時上址交通繁忙。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4186915/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"貨車故障不斷冒煙。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76b19af85b78f5fbe6210236c8f14bda/2025-04/01_2.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貨車故障不斷冒煙。fb：馬路的事討論區\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4186917/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"貨車故障不斷冒煙。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ac6864c897824d3b0fe03c45fa948a94/2025-04/03_2.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貨車故障不斷冒煙。fb：馬路的事討論區\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4186919/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"貨車故障不斷冒煙。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2c4f71c1e219d774171f4e73bf3b8afa/2025-04/05_3.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貨車故障不斷冒煙。fb：馬路的事討論區\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4186916/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場濃煙密佈。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e1c53d285c5d73402ad95a40ad0459be/2025-04/02_2.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場濃煙密佈。fb：馬路的事討論區\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4186918/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場濃煙密佈。fb：馬路的事討論區\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/283178e439c5dc6c10516a7b7eaf9004/2025-04/04_1.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場濃煙密佈。fb：馬路的事討論區\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
